### ============================================================
### 00. Keycloak + OpenFGA 초기 설정
### ============================================================
### [완전 초기화 순서]
### 1. infra 실행: cd infra && docker-compose up -d
### 2. OpenFGA 마이그레이션 (최초 1회):
###    docker run --rm --network infra_modu-erp openfga/openfga:latest \
###      migrate --datastore-engine postgres \
###      --datastore-uri "postgres://postgres:postgres@postgres:5432/openfga?sslmode=disable"
### 3. modu-erp realm 생성 (아래 요청 실행)
### 4. erp-organization 최초 기동 (store ID 없이):
###    ./gradlew :erp-organization:bootRun
###    → 로그에서 OPENFGA_STORE_ID 확인 후 Ctrl+C
### 5. erp-organization 2차 기동 (store ID만):
###    OPENFGA_STORE_ID=<id> ./gradlew :erp-organization:bootRun
###    → 로그에서 OPENFGA_MODEL_ID 확인 후 Ctrl+C
### 6. erp-organization 최종 기동 (두 ID 모두):
###    OPENFGA_STORE_ID=<id> OPENFGA_MODEL_ID=<id> ./gradlew :erp-organization:bootRun
### 7. admin 토큰 발급 (01-auth.http)
### ============================================================

### 1. Keycloak master 토큰 발급
# > 응답의 access_token 을 복사해둡니다
POST http://localhost:8180/realms/master/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=admin-cli&username=admin&password=admin

### 2. modu-erp realm 생성
# Authorization 헤더에 위에서 받은 access_token 입력
POST http://localhost:8180/admin/realms
Authorization: Bearer <master_access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realm": "modu-erp",
  "enabled": true,
  "registrationAllowed": false
}

### 3. (선택) realm 확인
GET http://localhost:8180/admin/realms/modu-erp
Authorization: Bearer <master_access_token>
